{"tid":1307274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉九龍灣「連儂牆」前襲兩人　46歲男子被控下周提堂","createTime":"2019-07-11T13:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:06:19.000Z","uid":135867,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a95bbf933016f1945cf1b09cea4ac3f6518d64a7","tid":1307274,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"涉九龍灣「連儂牆」前襲兩人　46歲男子被控下周提堂<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣淘大花園凌晨有兩名男子遇襲，一名46歲男子被捕，被控兩項襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪，下星期五在觀塘裁判法院提堂。根據網上片段，事發在凌晨，一名男子在淘大花園對面天橋底一幅「連儂牆」前，連續拳打另一名男子的臉部，遇襲男子一度倒地，再由其他人扶起。現場有目擊者多次勸阻，但涉案男子未有理會，又稱已經喝醉。警方其後到場拘捕涉嫌打人的46歲男子，該名男子同時涉嫌於同一地點，襲擊另一名65歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-11 20:50:00"},{"pid":"2258474e90917b0d4b82e1f7fa0957b4724c8af7","tid":1307274,"uid":43833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"洗定8月15入去坐啦"},{"pid":"445784e6367350019cdd9b8a4aea85a80eafeee9","tid":1307274,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"最少坐十二個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc040cf02fca46490d5a6d3114c439e55b9556a","tid":1307274,"uid":18845,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一路好走 <br />\n全撚部藍絲 都係垃圾"},{"pid":"94212fa9decd65308f6c83a77c9baa309b32e9bd","tid":1307274,"uid":45749,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"肥撚:屌，又話藍絲打人唔犯法嘅"},{"pid":"cbf749d328cc819dfdd241975a1077ad9e045ee2","tid":1307274,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1e4a2f558ad6ba541fae60b60713ad8160533f","tid":1307274,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"網上片段係咪唔可以做呈堂證供"},{"pid":"e65be6c28299c23d6cc1996eb99dc6040b65959f","tid":1307274,"uid":3615